    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait why cant i? i read online that if you miss a dose of lisinopril your levels drop and if you take a double dose it just brings it back up to where it's supposed to be. wouldnt it be better to just get it back to the therapeutic level immediately rather than waiting until tomorrow? i'm worried about the gap in coverage.",
